    <node id="Class 300 Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Class 300 Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 300 Flanges are described in ASME B16.5-2013 and are used in piping systems, with specific dimensions and tolerances provided.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanges are a specific type of flange mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 flanges are a specific class of flanges with certain pressure and temperature ratings.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanges are pipe flanges rated for a higher pressure class.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 flanges are described in detail in Table II-11, with specific dimensions provided.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 300 Flanges are a type of flange used in piping systems, specifically mentioned in relation to bolt hole templates.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1d1489d3ef80438a8abfd7382cf31328&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79c64f1efd29986d7f72185f69bc53da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99a1e3e75d92d69d9c4e1104e9aee33d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf07866fe1fa923d6c76315571aba601&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a46bab0c67076b2880139ab335aeabc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fddb3381428920d2982f42a7fcc67168&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24c021ba97b00541cab44ee6e76173ea</data>
