      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 1500 is a specific pressure-temperature rating in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 is a pressure rating class for flange facings, specified in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 is a classification for pipe flanges and法兰附件.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 refers to the dimensions and specifications for pipe flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 is a pressure rating class for ring-joint facings.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 refers to a specific class of pipe flanges with certain dimensional and material specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 1500 is a dimension standard for pipe fittings.</data>
