    <node id="Center-to-Contact Surface">
      <data key="d0">Center-to-Contact Surface</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Center-to-Contact Surface is a concept related to the dimensions of pipe fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface is a specific measurement in fittings dimensions.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface is the distance&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-contact surface dimensions are detailed in paragraphs 6.2.3 and 6.4.2.2.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-Contact Surface refers to a specific measurement dimension in fittings.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1c16e04b6fef5dddbccafe35258da63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7cf8cbd7624104560bfb71708f6cc010&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00bcbf709205575d1058a0d877e0be98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79385a11135d33465afc630658dca15b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfef7ffcc548c36b5c0ed0c4c060dedd</data>
