    <node id="Center-to-End Dimensions">
      <data key="d0">Center-to-End Dimensions</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Center-to-End Dimensions are the measurements from the center of a flange to its end.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-end dimensions refer to the measurements used in reducing fittings or end-to-end dimensions of reducers.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-End Dimensions are specific measurements in fittings dimensions.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-End Dimensions are specific measurements in fittings.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1c16e04b6fef5dddbccafe35258da63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a82ed5c06f52a3dac4b42b7d20165f5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-168613df3512c6ad1c5f5bdc4c21ec22&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00bcbf709205575d1058a0d877e0be98</data>
