    <node id="Drains">
      <data key="d0">Drains</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Drains are devices designed to remove water or other liquids from a space.&lt;SEP&gt;Drains are components designed to remove liquid from a system.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-1c16e04b6fef5dddbccafe35258da63d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4797fefc55d99753aacd5d36c1d642f3</data>
