    <node id="ASME International">
      <data key="d0">ASME International</data>
      <data key="d1">organization</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME International is a professional society and standards organization for the engineering and technology community. It is known for publishing and maintaining various ASME standards, including the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, which covers flanges,法兰, and pipe fittings. ASME International serves as the governing body overseeing the standard document ASME B16.5-2013 and provides the pressure-temperature ratings for materials, as well as the guidelines and standards for the material. Additionally, it is the copyright holder and provider of the document, the standards, and the guidelines mentioned in the text. ASME International also publishes other ASME standards such as ASME B36.10M.</data>
