      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Socket Welding is a connection method.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding is a method of joining pipes or tubes.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding is a method of joining flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding is a method of joining pipes where the fitting is inserted into a socket and then welded in place.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding is a technique used in joining pipes and fittings where the end of one piece is inserted into a socket in the other.</data>
