    <node id="Group 2.1 Materials">
      <data key="d0">Group 2.1 Materials</data>
      <data key="d1">category</data>
      <data key="d2">Group 2.1 Materials are a category of materials with specific pressure and temperature ratings.&lt;SEP&gt;Group 2.1 Materials are the materials discussed in Table 2-2.1 of the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Group 2.1 Materials refers to the materials listed in the table.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-a0109166d44b4066c639726c7a8ccb61&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bdc0d4cce7bb0fdac95a4097088eb542&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-656b6734cce47f14e81f0e8c31c77d35</data>
