    <node id="Base Elbow">
      <data key="d0">Base Elbow</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Base Elbow is a type of flanged fitting used in piping systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Elbow is a type of flanged fitting described in the table.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Elbow is a type of flanged fitting mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Elbow is a type of fitting mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Elbow is a type of flanged fitting that connects pipes at a 90-degree angle with a round or square base.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5a2d9b2e3cbcac399e69cd4ddd026d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76864809d8f49cc522affb8d29d2289a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b3183da68eed473652f2a88bb963447&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d62708c76d7807fe7760eab56bea6043&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38e654cf4e95cce3ba3e7cced9c476f4</data>
