    <node id="Spot Facing">
      <data key="d0">Spot Facing</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Spot Facing is a machining technique used to remove material from a localized area of a flange or fitting, creating a flat surface. This process is essential for ensuring a tight fit and a secure seal between flanges. According to the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, spot facing details are provided in paragraph 6.6, which covers the preparation of flange edges to enhance sealing performance. Spot facing is also mentioned as a relevant topic in documents related to pipe flanges, emphasizing its importance in achieving precise and reliable connections. This machining operation involves creating a smooth surface on the flange, typically to prepare it for welding or bolting, thereby ensuring a tight seal.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-4797fefc55d99753aacd5d36c1d642f3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7ea1b2e76d1f000d5569b9486b9e5ac4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98e6bd64e65f31d06ced3b3e90f47312&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-edfa2a8d33668f4d57dbfceea1fab17e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-65bb92edfd06205fa901097f136f3ce0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-00bcbf709205575d1058a0d877e0be98&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c860be0c3f5ab97837a33d0776f228db&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3e063d28a217c52dd27cce9855642fcf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3d3983136bf26d485546eb760e1ee8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bfef7ffcc548c36b5c0ed0c4c060dedd</data>
      <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
      <data key="d5">1776255072</data>
      <data key="d6" />
    </node>
    <node id="Base Tee">
      <data key="d0">Base Tee</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Base Tee is a type of flanged fitting used in piping systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Tee is a type of flanged fitting included in the table.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Tee is a type of flanged fitting mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Tee is a type of fitting mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Tee is a type of pipe fitting used in plumbing and piping systems.&lt;SEP&gt;Base Tee is a type of flanged fitting that connects three pipes at a tee configuration with a round or square base.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5a2d9b2e3cbcac399e69cd4ddd026d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76864809d8f49cc522affb8d29d2289a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b3183da68eed473652f2a88bb963447&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d62708c76d7807fe7760eab56bea6043&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38e654cf4e95cce3ba3e7cced9c476f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7d66f91fd341a23e68eadbefdb9b7ab</data>
