    <node id="Round Base">
      <data key="d0">Round Base</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Round Base is a type of base used in flanged fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base is a type of flanged fitting described in the table&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base is a base design for some fittings that is circular in shape.&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base is a type of base mentioned in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base is a type of fitting base mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base is a type of base intended for support in compression, not for anchors or supports in tension or shear.&lt;SEP&gt;Round Base refers to the base design of a flanged fitting with a round shape.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-5a2d9b2e3cbcac399e69cd4ddd026d10&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-79c64f1efd29986d7f72185f69bc53da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76864809d8f49cc522affb8d29d2289a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2b3183da68eed473652f2a88bb963447&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d62708c76d7807fe7760eab56bea6043&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-38e654cf4e95cce3ba3e7cced9c476f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55a057d80d0d30bec149f947f43931d5</data>
