      <data key="d2">Pressure–Temperature Ratings are data points indicating the maximum pressure and temperature limits for various materials.&lt;SEP&gt;Pressure–Temperature Ratings describe the operational limits of a component.&lt;SEP&gt;Pressure–Temperature Ratings are specifications for various materials.&lt;SEP&gt;Pressure–Temperature Ratings are specifications for materials in terms of their performance under various pressure and temperature conditions.</data>
