    <node id="Reducing Slip-On Flange">
      <data key="d0">Reducing Slip-On Flange</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">A reducing slip-on flange is a type of flange that reduces the pipe size and is attached by slipping over the pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Slip-On Flange is a type of pipe flange that reduces the size of the pipe.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-2904771c0741938726758dab221ea2fd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0c2f5be5ae1269254713641c236d6a28</data>
