      <data key="d0">Threaded Flange</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Threaded Flange is a type of pipe flange that uses threads for connection.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded Flange is a type of flange that uses threads for connection.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded Flange is a type of flange with screw threads for joining pipes.</data>
