      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">A hub is a central part of a flange that connects to the pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub is a central part of a flange that connects to the pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub is a component of the flange mentioned in the table.&lt;SEP&gt;A hub is mentioned in the context of flanges, specifically in relation to its diameter and taper.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub is a part of a flange that connects to the pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Hub is a component of the flange described in the document.</data>
