    <node id="Reducing Welding Neck Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Reducing Welding Neck Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Reducing Welding Neck Flanges are pipe fittings that allow for reducing the size of the pipe and provide a welding neck connection.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing welding neck flanges are discussed in para 6.8.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing welding neck flanges are covered in paragraph 6.8 of the ASME B16.5-2013 standard.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Welding Neck Flanges are described in the document and have specific dimensions.&lt;SEP&gt;Reducing Welding Neck Flanges are types of flanges used to reduce the size of a pipe connection and have a neck for welding.</data>
