      <data key="d2">Socket Welding Flanges are a type of flange with specific counterbore size requirements.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket welding flanges are mentioned as having Class 600 dimensions and can be provided for NPS sizes ranging from 1/2 to 2 1/2.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding Flanges are pipe fittings where the fitting is socket-welded to the pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Socket welding flanges may&lt;SEP&gt;Socket Welding Flanges are a type of pipe flange designed for socket welding connections.</data>
