    <node id="Class 150 Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Class 150 Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 150 Flanges are a specific type of flange with standardized dimensions as detailed in Table 8.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are described in ASME B16.5-2013 and have specific dimensions and tolerances.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 flanges are a specific class of flanges with certain pressure and temperature ratings.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are pipe flanges rated for a specific pressure class.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, detailing their dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanges are a specific class of flanges with a pressure rating of 150 pounds per square inch.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-b120c00906326354cc4b07e8df4a85b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55e62fdaeb2f89ecf30d7410c3be1d43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a46bab0c67076b2880139ab335aeabc3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2ee06a2df0130f4a0dc8ec87fdc1d0c4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fddb3381428920d2982f42a7fcc67168&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05f0bcb59476ec9c3e973721c57f3c96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-24c021ba97b00541cab44ee6e76173ea</data>
