    <node id="ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code">
      <data key="d0">ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code</data>
      <data key="d1">standard</data>
      <data key="d2">ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code is a code for welding procedures and qualification.&lt;SEP&gt;The ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code is a standard for the design, fabrication, inspection, and testing of boilers, pressure vessels, and related accessories.&lt;SEP&gt;The ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code provides standards for the design, fabrication, inspection, and testing of boilers and pressure vessels.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-fa036517d95c30255cdfda4bb900973d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f7d037c7aa1de140eef228e3b5f72b1a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-163392eb949c4d866fc3a6cbdb8233ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dc67612f135316380b75df378379082b</data>
