    <node id="Class 150 Flanged Fittings">
      <data key="d0">Class 150 Flanged Fittings</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Class 150 Flanged Fittings are described in ASME B16.5-2013 and have specific dimensions and tolerances.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanged Fittings are pipe fittings with a specific pressure rating.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanged Fittings are described in the ASME B16.5-2013 standard, detailing their dimensions and specifications.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanged Fittings are fittings designed to withstand a maximum working pressure of 150 pounds per square inch.&lt;SEP&gt;Class 150 Flanged Fittings are specific types of pipe fittings with a pressure rating of 150 pounds per square inch.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-55e62fdaeb2f89ecf30d7410c3be1d43&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-76864809d8f49cc522affb8d29d2289a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-05f0bcb59476ec9c3e973721c57f3c96&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-55a057d80d0d30bec149f947f43931d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-944868763ad488938d4bbbf02d4db395</data>
