      <data key="d2">Center-to-End is a measurement concept used in flanged fittings dimensions.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-End refers to a measurement or dimension in the context of flanged fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-End is a measurement related to the dimensions of pipe fittings.&lt;SEP&gt;Center-to-End is a measurement used in pipe fittings.</data>
