    <node id="Threaded Flanges">
      <data key="d0">Threaded Flanges</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Threaded Flanges are pipe flanges with threaded ends, allowing for screw-in connections.&lt;SEP&gt;Threaded flanges are a type of flange where the connection is made through threading.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-f28c7d4bdd4e434720bb2e0817acb7da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d8ab581faa40c9c1eb52a6a9307019c</data>
