    <node id="Slip-On Welding">
      <data key="d0">Slip-On Welding</data>
      <data key="d1">method</data>
      <data key="d2">Slip-On Welding is a method of joining flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Slip-On Welding is a method of attaching a flange to a pipe by welding.&lt;SEP&gt;Slip-On Welding is a type of pipe fitting where the fitting is slipped onto the pipe and then welded in place.&lt;SEP&gt;Slip-On Welding is a method of joining pipes where the fitting is slipped over the end of the pipe and then welded in place.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-99a1e3e75d92d69d9c4e1104e9aee33d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31bc32875a6306edfc4741462637a4e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45ef876ea0243f68770603a1cadf892b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0df2a48018c5815fcbc69ee77e5e9629</data>
