    <node id="Welding Neck">
      <data key="d0">Welding Neck</data>
      <data key="d1">artifact</data>
      <data key="d2">Welding Neck is a type of flange joint mentioned in the document.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding Neck is a type of flange neck used in pipe connections.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding Neck is a type of pipe fitting that has a short section of pipe attached to the main pipe, allowing for easier welding.&lt;SEP&gt;Welding Neck is a type of flange with a short neck for welding.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-99a1e3e75d92d69d9c4e1104e9aee33d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-31bc32875a6306edfc4741462637a4e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-0df2a48018c5815fcbc69ee77e5e9629&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6b3b645868407aac7a7956cba998d0e5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-45ef876ea0243f68770603a1cadf892b</data>
