    <node id="Inside Diameter">
      <data key="d0">Inside Diameter</data>
      <data key="d1">concept</data>
      <data key="d2">Inside Diameter is the internal measurement of a pipe.&lt;SEP&gt;Inside diameter is a specific dimension for welding ends of welding neck flanges and smaller bore of socket welding flanges.&lt;SEP&gt;Inside Diameter refers to the internal measurement of a pipe or joint.&lt;SEP&gt;Inside Diameter is a concept referring to the inner measurement of a pipe or component.</data>
