      <data key="d3">chunk-1c16e04b6fef5dddbccafe35258da63d</data>
      <data key="d2">For the center-to-end dimensions of reducing fittings or end-to-end dimensions of reducers, use center-to-flange edge or flange edge-to-flange edge dimensions for the largest opening, and add the proper height to provide for ring joint groove applying to each flange.</data>
