    <edge source="IHS" target="ASME B16.5-2013">
      <data key="d7">21.0</data>
      <data key="d8">ASME B16.5-2013 is a standard distributed and licensed by IHS under agreement with ASME International. IHS provides access to this standard document through a licensing arrangement with ASME International. Both ASME B16.5-2013 and its licensed copies are distributed by IHS, ensuring that users have access to the standard under the terms of the license. IHS acts as the distributor and licensor, providing the necessary permissions for the document to be accessed and used. This relationship between ASME B16.5-2013 and IHS involves a clear licensing framework where IHS is responsible for distributing the standard under the terms granted by ASME International.</data>
      <data key="d9">access provision,data provision,distribution,document distribution,document provider,license,license agreement,licensing,organization,publication,standard document</data>
